{"tid":197892,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"一念無明小明做左耶撚","createTime":"2017-04-12T07:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T09:00:42.000Z","uid":21746,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eebdd1c673636b1e3521155a09f36ea3b9dff385","tid":197892,"uid":21746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T07:29:25.000Z","msg":"冇記錯應該係基督教 唔係天主教下話？<br />\n前幾日見到網上有篇文讚小明演繹到女人渴望成家 就快達成願望之時點知瞬間跌落低谷嘅怨恨同難過<br />\n但有冇人同我一樣覺得唔多唔少想暗諷宗教嘅意義？<br />\n耶撚成日同人講寬恕別人 但小明喺教會似想擺fisherman lok上檯控訴佢<br />\n所以宗教幫唔幫到人釋懷呢？定抑或只係透過表面嘅寬恕 去legitimise怨恨？<br />\n如果做到完全寬恕 又洗唔洗每個禮拜日圍爐重提往日嘅怨恨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c6fb53387d2b50c5ba0e54ec51d13d4792fd2c","tid":197892,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T07:41:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df3536e2e2da556eded1199770557b3501ca7f59","tid":197892,"uid":34471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T07:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18397bd46601135df407a53de650853735b637d7","tid":197892,"uid":21746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T08:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果d 阿們好似撞邪</blockquote><br />\n我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0acc09ddfc62d82c7a155055dd969d574412a82a","tid":197892,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T08:10:32.000Z","msg":"根本係串鳩緊班耶撚虛偽"},{"pid":"5cc7a0cfd2a0734113158544c8818165378d537d","tid":197892,"uid":89999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T08:11:19.000Z","msg":"都唔係暗諷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503d22c9a51b182a0c3b3b11e416b430419af5bf","tid":197892,"uid":60790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T08:15:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果d 阿們好似撞邪</blockquote><br />\n我睇個陣都呢個位笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor